Sorry I mistaken ?

My previous script won?t work because drc does not have a function called hill().
That line 

fct = hill(names = c("Top", "Bottom", "Kd", "nH"))

Here is the correct way in drc with LL.4

library(drc)

hill_mod <- drm(
  Response ~ Dose,
  data = df,
  fct = LL.4(names = c("Bottom", "Top", "Kd", "nH"))
)

